```

### ‚úÖ **2.2 - V√©rification**
```sql
-- V√©rifier que les colonnes sont cr√©√©es
SELECT column_name FROM information_schema.columns 
WHERE table_name = 'fiches' AND column_name LIKE 'exemple_%'
ORDER BY column_name;
```

